<section class="page-section" style="background: var(--surface-2);">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>The BridgeDegree Journey — Step by Step</h2>
    <div class="journey-timeline">
      <div class="journey-item">
        <h3>Step 1 — Create Your BridgeDegree Application</h3>
        <p>When you join BridgeDegree, you begin by completing a short Career Assessment.</p>
        <p>This helps us understand:</p>
        <p>Your academic background<br />Your career interests<br />Your existing skills<br />Your long-term goals (local career, remote work, or global opportunities)</p>
        <p>Using this information, we create your BridgeDegree Career Passport, a verified professional identity that tracks your skills, projects, internships, and achievements throughout your university journey.</p>
        <p>Your Career Passport becomes your verifiable employability profile for employers, universities, and global recruiters.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="journey-item">
        <h3>Step 2 — Get Matched With a Mentor</h3>
        <p>Once your assessment is complete, BridgeDegree assigns you a mentorship programme.</p>
        <p>Your mentor helps you:</p>
        <p>Identify the right career path early<br />Build relevant skills for your industry<br />Prepare for internships and professional projects<br />Develop a strong professional identity</p>
        <p>Depending on your goals, you may be matched with:</p>
        <p>A Career Mentor to guide your professional development<br />An Industry Mentor working in your target field<br />A Research Mentor for academic publications<br />A Global Pathway Mentor for study or work abroad</p>
        <p>Mentors ensure you are not navigating your career blindly during university.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="journey-item">
        <h3>Step 3 — Start Building Real Work Experience</h3>
        <p>From 200 Level onward, BridgeDegree connects you with structured industry opportunities.</p>
        <p>These include:</p>
        <p>Virtual internships with Nigerian companies<br />Remote projects with international organizations<br />Real industry briefs aligned with your course of study<br />Employer-reviewed project deliverables</p>
        <p>Every placement is verified and recorded in your Career Passport, giving you documented professional experience before graduation.</p>
        <p>By the time you finish university, you may have 2+ years of verifiable work experience.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="journey-item">
        <h3>Step 4 — Turn Academic Work Into Real Research Output</h3>
        <p>In most universities, final-year projects end up sitting in libraries.</p>
        <p>BridgeDegree transforms them into publishable research and industry solutions.</p>
        <p>Through our Academic Output Engine, students can:</p>
        <p>Co-author academic publications with lecturers<br />Align final-year projects with real industry problems<br />Contribute to research that can be cited globally</p>
        <p>This creates an academic footprint that strengthens your career, scholarship applications, and global credibility.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="journey-item">
        <h3>Step 5 — Build Your Global Career Pathway</h3>
        <p>BridgeDegree also prepares students for global opportunities early.</p>
        <p>Instead of rushing into visa applications after graduation, students receive structured preparation during their degree.</p>
        <p>This includes:</p>
        <p>Scholarship research and planning<br />International CV and portfolio development<br />Visa pathway intelligence<br />Remote work preparation<br />Global workplace communication training</p>
        <p>By the time you graduate, you are admission-ready, job-ready, and globally competitive.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="journey-item">
        <h3>Step 6 — Graduate With a Career — Not Just a Degree</h3>
        <p>When students complete the BridgeDegree journey, they graduate with:</p>
        <p>Verified work experience<br />Published research or industry projects<br />A strong professional portfolio<br />Mentor recommendations<br />A global career pathway strategy</p>
        <p>Your Career Passport becomes a trusted credential that employers and institutions can verify instantly.</p>
        <p>You leave university with something far more powerful than a certificate — you leave with career leverage.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

